description: The water views from this lovely 2bed/2bath Penthouse in South Boston are only the beginning!  Located on the downslope of Thomas Park, the beach is only a block away!  Boasting over 1000sf over two floors, choose from one of two en suite bedrooms- they both have water views!  Enjoy the cozy living room with fireplace, a chef's kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors throughout and tons of natural sunlight.  This home also features 2 private outdoor spaces- a deck off the bedroom looking over Carson Bay, and a rear deck off the living room, ideal for outdoor dining and entertaining.  Fully equipped with an in unit washer/dryer, central AC, and two full bathrooms.  One block from the beach, and three blocks from Broadway- everything you need within a 1/2 mile radius!
